description:
We all saw Kylie Worthy in her Tag Team debut, weighing in at 5'7" and 145lbs. She's strong and has a good understanding of US style wrestling. Her tag team was victorious and she gained valuable experience in the win.
The Butcher, 5'2" 109lbs, surprised us all with a 1 pt win over fan favorite Spartica. Madison has strong wrestling skills and is a demon on the mat.
The classic David vs Goliath, except Goliath is a hot tan shaved blond with huge tits and nipples, and David is a little demon spawn from hell bent on kicking every ones ass on the mat.
** Watching the Butcher bind the Terminator and tickle her in RD4 is worth the price of admission alone!
title: Kylie Worthy "The Terminator" (0-0)
